  "description": "The youngest of a family of distinguished warriors, Vivica knew she had to do something special to get out from the shadows of her seven older brothers. When she was offered her first, child-sized sword, she wrinkled her nose and grabbed the largest greatsword she could lift.\n\nWielding the blade was gruelling work, but the discouragement of her family members only fuelled Vivica's fire. To their amazement, she could soon wield a blade as tall as she was as with unnatural speed.",
